233
00:17:41,394 --> 00:17:42,895
Apa?

234
00:17:44,647 --> 00:17:47,024
Baiklah, ayo.

235
00:17:51,404 --> 00:17:53,281
Aku mencetak gol hari ini.

236
00:17:53,364 --> 00:17:54,907
Astaga, kau hebat.

237
00:17:56,701 --> 00:17:58,911
- Begitu saja?
- Nenek harus berkata apa lagi?

238
00:17:58,995 --> 00:18:01,122
Nenek berkata "kau hebat"
karena memang begitu.

239
00:18:01,205 --> 00:18:03,749
Astaga, Nenek.

240
