"You are a boy."

464
00:32:40,167 --> 00:32:42,419
"You are a boy."

465
00:32:42,502 --> 00:32:44,629
Oke, kalian semua hebat.

466
00:32:44,713 --> 00:32:47,299
Sekarang mari kita berlatih bersama. Oke?

467
00:32:49,342 --> 00:32:51,928
Apa yang baru dikatakan orang Barat itu?

468
00:32:54,264 --> 00:32:55,682
Bu Guru.

469
00:32:55,765 --> 00:32:59,394
Bicaralah dalam bahasa kami.
Aku tidak paham sepatah kata pun.

470
00:33:01,605 --> 00:33:02,981
Apa katamu barusan?

471
00:33:03,064 --> 00:33:07,736
Bagaimana mungkin aku tiba-tiba
berbicara bahasa Joseon?

472
00:33:07,819 --> 00:33:09,321
Oh, ya Tuhan!

473
00:33:10,363 --> 00:33:11,656
TAHUN 1970

474
00:33:11,781 --> 00:33:12,908
KOMIK
BELA DIRI, ROMANSA

475
00:33:12,991 --> 00:33:15,494
DOMBA HITAM SANG BANGSAWAN
EPISODE TERAKHIR

476
00:33:22,125 --> 00:33:23,585
TAMAT

477
00:33:23,668 --> 00:33:24,628
Apa?

478
00:33:25,462 --> 00:33:27,547
Tokoh utamanya mati?

479
00:33:30,926 --> 00:33:33,136
Akhir cerita macam apa ini?

480
00:33:33,220 --> 00:33:34,554
Hei, Pak Komikus.

481
00:33:35,138 --> 00:33:36,181
Pak Komikus!

482
00:33:39,893 --> 00:33:41,353
Siapa kau?

483
00:33:43,188 --> 00:33:44,523
Kenapa akhir kisahnya begini?

484
